text: Ataur Rahman is a Jatiya Samajtantrik Dal-JSD politician and the former Member of Parliament of Sirajganj-3. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Sirajganj-3 in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Samajtantrik Dal-JSD politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Ataur Rahman (politician)
